---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Vampire Crawlers Elements Guide — Blood, Frost, Shadow, Lightning Explained (2026)';
const description = 'Complete Vampire Crawlers elemental system guide. How Blood, Frost, Shadow, and Lightning elements work, elemental synergies, bonuses, and which element is best.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical="https://vampcrawlers.cc/guides/elements-guide">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Vampire Crawlers Elements Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Master the four elements — Blood, Frost, Shadow, and Lightning — and their synergies.</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-3">Blood Element — Lifesteal & Sustain</h2>
        <p>Blood is the most forgiving element, perfect for beginners. Blood cards heal you while dealing damage. The 3-card synergy grants <strong>+15% lifesteal for 8 seconds</strong>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Best for:</strong> Long runs, boss fights, learning the game.</p>
        <p><strong>Weakness:</strong> Lower burst damage than Shadow or Lightning.</p>
        <p><strong>Counters:</strong> Neutral — effective against all elements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Frost Element — Crowd Control & Defense</h2>
        <p>Frost controls the battlefield by freezing enemies. Frozen enemies cannot move or attack. The 3-card synergy makes your <strong>next hit freeze the target</strong> regardless of the card used.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Best for:</strong> High difficulty floors, swarms of enemies.</p>
        <p><strong>Weakness:</strong> Lower raw damage, relies on setup.</p>
        <p><strong>Strong against:</strong> Lightning enemies. <strong>Weak against:</strong> Fire enemies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">Shadow Element — Burst & Mobility</h2>
        <p>Shadow is the highest skill-cap element. Shadow cards enable teleportation, critical hits, and massive single-target damage. The 3-card synergy grants <strong>+50% crit chance for 6 seconds</strong>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Best for:</strong> Speed clears, boss killing, experienced players.</p>
        <p><strong>Weakness:</strong> Low survivability, punishing if you make mistakes.</p>
        <p><strong>Strong against:</strong> Blood enemies. <strong>Weak against:</strong> Light/Holy enemies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-3">Lightning Element — AoE & Speed</h2>
        <p>Lightning is the fastest clearing element. Cards chain between enemies and provide attack speed buffs. The 3-card synergy grants <strong>+30% attack speed for 8 seconds</strong>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Best for:</strong> Wave clearing, farming runs.</p>
        <p><strong>Weakness:</strong> Low single-target damage, glass cannon playstyle.</p>
        <p><strong>Strong against:</strong> Water enemies. <strong>Weak against:</strong> Earth enemies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Dual-Element Strategy</h2>
        <p>The strongest builds typically use <strong>two elements</strong>. A primary element for damage and a secondary for utility. Recommended pairings:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-400">
          <li><strong>Blood + Shadow</strong> — Sustain from Blood, burst from Shadow. The most popular competitive build.</li>
          <li><strong>Frost + Lightning</strong> — Freeze enemies then blast them with chain lightning.</li>
          <li><strong>Frost + Shadow</strong> — Freeze a priority target, then Shadow Strike for 3x damage via Shatter.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm">
      <a href="/guides/best-builds" class="text-red-400 hover:underline">Best Builds</a>
      <a href="/guides/card-combos" class="text-red-400 hover:underline">Card Combos</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
